Informations de dépendance

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>com.objis.mavenapps</groupId>
  <artifactId>monappli</artifactId>
  <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'com.objis.mavenapps:monappli:jar:1.0-SNAPSHOT'

Apache Ivy

<dependency org="com.objis.mavenapps" name="monappli" rev="1.0-SNAPSHOT">
  <artifact name="monappli" type="jar" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='com.objis.mavenapps', module='monappli', version='1.0-SNAPSHOT')
)

Gradle/Grails

compile 'com.objis.mavenapps:monappli:1.0-SNAPSHOT'

Scala SBT

libraryDependencies += "com.objis.mavenapps" % "monappli" % "1.0-SNAPSHOT"

Leiningen

[com.objis.mavenapps/monappli "1.0-SNAPSHOT"]
